First load a database, then, if needed, load files. Tips:

  • Click object names to see content
  • Click Query Editor to write custom queries; each query must end with a semicolon.
  • First column must be a primary key number for table updates to work. Otherwise write select statement so it is.
  • Load csv file: create virtual table tablename using vsv(filename=thefilename.csv);
  • To delete files: select util_deletefile('path/filename')
  • the database to save changes.
